---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import BreadcrumbSchema from '../components/schema/BreadcrumbSchema.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Perfume Picks terms of service — eligibility, subscriptions, user-generated content, affiliate disclosure, and limitation of liability."
  path="/terms"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <BreadcrumbSchema crumbs={[{ name: 'Terms of Service', url: `${SITE.url}/terms` }]} />
  </Fragment>

  <p class="brand">{SITE.name}</p>
  <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
  <p class="effective">Effective Date: May 13, 2026</p>

  <p>
    These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of Perfume Picks ("the
    app") and the website at <a href={SITE.url}>{SITE.url}</a>. By using the
    app or the website, you agree to these Terms.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
  <p>
    You must be at least 13 years of age to use Perfume Picks. By creating an
    account or using the app, you represent that you meet this age requirement.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Account and Sign-In</h2>
  <p>
    You may sign in with Apple or Google, or continue as a guest. You are
    responsible for activity under your account. Guest accounts store data
    locally on your device; signing in enables cloud sync across devices.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Subscriptions</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>Perfume Picks Pro</strong> is an optional auto-renewing
    subscription available as a monthly or yearly plan. Subscriptions are
    managed by Apple through the App Store and processed by RevenueCat as our
    subscription manager. Key terms:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Pricing is shown in-app at the time of purchase, in your local currency.</li>
    <li>Payment is charged to your Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase.</li>
    <li>Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.</li>
    <li>You can manage subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal in <strong>Settings &rarr; Apple ID &rarr; Subscriptions</strong> on your iPhone.</li>
    <li>Refund requests must be made through Apple. We cannot process refunds directly.</li>
    <li>Price changes take effect at the next renewal and require notice and consent where required by Apple.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Free vs Pro</h2>
  <p>
    The Free tier is feature-limited; Pro unlocks additional features.
    Current pricing and the up-to-date list of what each tier includes are
    shown in-app at the time of purchase and may evolve as new features
    ship. Continued use of an active subscription after a feature change
    constitutes acceptance of the updated tier definition.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Affiliate Links and Retailer Disclosure</h2>
  <p>
    Fragrance detail pages and selected articles may include
    <strong>&ldquo;Buy from&rdquo;</strong> links to third-party retailers
    such as FragranceX, Sephora, Amazon Luxury Beauty, and others. These are
    affiliate links: when you click one and complete a purchase, we may earn
    a small commission from the retailer. <strong>This does not affect the
    price you pay.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    Affiliate links are clearly indicated on the page where they appear.
    Perfume Picks is not a retailer and does not sell, distribute, or ship
    fragrance. Your purchase contract is with the retailer, and any questions
    about pricing, shipping, returns, or product authenticity must be
    directed to them.
  </p>
  <p>
    This disclosure is provided in accordance with the FTC's
    <em>Guides Concerning the Use of Endorsements and Testimonials in Advertising</em>.
  </p>

  <h2>6. User Content</h2>
  <p>
    You retain ownership of content you create on Perfume Picks, including
    wear logs, ratings, private notes, SOTD posts, and any reviews. By
    submitting a Scent of the Day post or any other content that you make
    public, you grant Perfume Picks a non-exclusive, royalty-free, worldwide
    license to host, display, and distribute that content within the app and
    on the website for the purpose of operating the service.
  </p>
  <p>
    You may delete your public content at any time. Private notes and wear
    logs remain solely under your control and are not licensed to us beyond
    what is necessary to operate the app.
  </p>
  <p>
    You agree not to submit content that is unlawful, defamatory, obscene,
    harassing, abusive, objectionable, or infringes on the intellectual
    property rights of others. We have zero tolerance for objectionable
    content or abusive behavior.
  </p>
  <p>
    Any user can report content through the in-app "Report" button. We review
    reports within 24 hours and will remove violating content and, where
    appropriate, restrict or terminate the offending account. We reserve the
    right to remove content at our discretion.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Recommendations</h2>
  <p>
    Picks, similarity matches, layering suggestions, and dupe suggestions are
    best-effort, based on catalog data and our taste-profile model. Personal
    scent perception varies. Always sample before purchasing a full bottle.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Acceptable Use</h2>
  <p>
    No abuse, scraping, reverse-engineering, or interference with the service.
    We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Intellectual Property</h2>
  <p>
    The Perfume Picks name, logo, design, and code are our property. Fragrance
    brand names, house names, product names, and bottle imagery are the
    property of their respective owners and are used for informational and
    identification purposes only.
  </p>

  <h2>10. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
  <p>
    Perfume Picks is provided "AS IS" and "AS AVAILABLE" without warranties
    of any kind, express or implied. Fragrance notes, accords, and
    performance information are general reference and may not reflect every
    batch or reformulation. We make no claims about the safety, suitability,
    or compatibility of any fragrance with any individual's skin or health.
    If you have a known fragrance sensitivity or allergy, consult the
    retailer or manufacturer before purchasing.
  </p>

  <h2>11. Limitation of Liability</h2>
  <p>
    To the maximum extent permitted by law, our total liability for any claim
    related to the app or the website shall not exceed the amount you paid to
    us in the prior twelve months. We are not liable for any indirect,
    incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from or
    related to your use of the service, including loss of data.
  </p>

  <h2>12. Account Deletion</h2>
  <p>
    You may delete your account at any time from the Profile screen within
    the app. This permanently removes all your data and cannot be undone.
    Deleting your account does not automatically cancel an active App Store
    subscription &mdash; manage subscriptions in
    <strong>Settings &rarr; Apple ID &rarr; Subscriptions</strong>.
  </p>

  <h2>13. Changes to These Terms</h2>
  <p>
    We may update these Terms from time to time. Material changes will be
    communicated through the app. Continued use after changes constitutes
    acceptance of the revised Terms.
  </p>

  <h2>14. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For questions about these Terms, contact us at:
    <a href={`mailto:${SITE.supportEmail}`}>{SITE.supportEmail}</a>
  </p>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
